history.content:
There is not a piazza for IEOR, but there is a department wide slack.

berkeleyieor.slack.com

There is also the slack for the Institute of Industrial and Systems Engineers (IISE). They host events, give course advice, and are a great community!

If you are interested in joining IISE, fill out this form!
